<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavarṣaṁbulu 1313 gunēṁṭi jyēṣṭa kṛṣṇa 10 varanidhivārāna
<lb n="2" break="no"/>nu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> kaḷiṁgaparīkṣa mahā<supplied reason="omitted">pā</supplied>tra śrīcaṁppuḍuḷḷadāku māranāyakāṇi garuḍa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>nāyakāṇi tanaku nabhīṣṭarttasiddhigānu śrīnārasiṁhyanātu nityamu 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>nu rēpaṭi dūpavasaramu venakanu Āragiṁppanu [maḍapali Okaṭi]
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ya pappucīḍi Okaṭi samarppi<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>ccenu Iṁddulaku narasiṁhyanāya
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ka purāInāIni vaśānanu gaṁḍalu Iruvai <unclear>mā</unclear>ḍalu Icce
<lb n="7" break="no"/>nu Iṁddulāvāṟikini yēṁṭanu muppaiyaṟupuṭlu <unclear>kolpuṁ</unclear>nnureṁ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ḍu puṭluṁnu Enamaṁdumuḷi pesalunnu śrī bhāṁḍāra<unclear>maṁ</unclear>du
<lb n="9"/>vasamucēyaṁgalaṁḍu naṁbyāḷumāna parisarakulu mānaki
<lb n="10" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ṛla varadaya dupakaḷamaṁdu dīpanibaṁdamu Aḍapurāyi
<lb n="11" break="no"/>nāyuṁḍu Adiṣṭānamu prasādamu 1 kuṁca pavucīḍi 1 I dharmmu
<lb n="12"/>śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrīśrīśrī
</p>

